body:
@Nouman97 Did you convert the longformer model to onnx format? If so, please share the conversion script so that I could see whether the onnxruntime optimizer need some change to handle longformer onnx model. 

If not, I would suggest to start with the conversion to onnx. You can follow the notebook to do that. Also, there is a tool in huggingface transformer: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers/blob/master/src/transformers/convert_graph_to_onnx.py. You may modify it by replacing the AutoModel to LongformerModel.

The Attention operator will support 2D attention mask in the coming onnxruntime 1.4.0. I think it is possible to help longformer.
